<div>
        <form class="form-horizontal"> <span style="position:relative; top:0px; left:670px; float: left;"><a href="http://wiki.openseamap.org/wiki/De:Metadata_help" target="_blank"><img src="images/help.png" width="32" height="32"/></a></span>
 <legend data-trt="1069:Sensor Positions"></legend>
            <p>
           Sounder sensor and GPS antenna normally exist at different places on the ship. The position of the sensors and not the positionn of the displays is important. The ship is viewed from above.
            </p>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="span8">
                    <div class="control-group">
                        <label class="control-label" for="idDepthDisplayed">Position of sounder</label>
                        <div class="controls">
                            <label class="checkbox">
                                <input type="checkbox" name="echoSounderInFront" value="1" id="echoSounderInFront" {{echoSounderInFront}} > behind the GPS antenna (closer to the nose)
                            </label>
                            <label class="checkbox">
                                <input type="checkbox" name="echoSounderRightOf" value="1" id="echoSounderRightOf" {{echoSounderRightOf}} > right from the GPS antenna (more to the bow side)
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="control-group">
                        <label class="control-label" for="distanceY">Distance lengthwise</label>
                        <div class="controls">
                            <div class="input-append">
                                <input type="text" id="distanceY" class="input-mini" name="distanceY" id="distanceY" value="{{distanceY}}" placeholder="0.00"/>
                                <span class="add-on">m</span>
							      </div>	  <span class="help-inline"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
    <div class="control-group">
                        <label class="control-label" for="distanceX">Distance crosswise</label>
                        <div class="controls">
                            <div class="input-append">
                                <input type="text" class="input-mini" name="distanceX" id="distanceX" value="{{distanceX}}" placeholder="0.00"/>
                                <span class="add-on">m</span>
								  <span class="help-inline"></span>
                            </div>	  <span class="help-inline"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="span4">
                    <div id="oseam-canvas" class="oseam-canvas"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
         </form>
    </div>